data.title: Xianbei Stat1
data.meta_description: Xianbei Stat1 - Free ebook download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document discusses the history of two Khanates in northern Afghanistan - Andkhui Khanate and Badakhshan. It provides lists of the Khans of Andkhui Khanate from 1730 to 1880 and the rulers of Badakhshan from 1145 to 1589, including various dynasties such as Shansabanids, Timurid and local rulers. It also lists the later Mirs or rulers of Badakhshan from 1657 to 1765 under the Yarid dynasty.
